locality: K6, Kijiado District. Olopolos. On the Nairobi-Magadi Rd.

Hills 5 km W of village. Rough hillocky surface, sandy soil, much disturbed by cutting & charcoal-making. Thinned woodland with shrubbery, 3-10m high, mostly Commiphora spp, also Combretum, Terminalia, Vitex, Catunaregam, Grewia, others.
